      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>於我乎，夏屋渠渠，今也每食無餘。于嗟乎！不承權輿。
於我乎，每食四簋，今也每食不飽。于嗟乎！不承權輿。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>1 He assigned us a house large and spacious;
But now at every meal there is nothing left.
Alas that he could not continue as he began!

2 He assigned us at every meal four dishes of grain;
But now at every meal we do not get our fill.
Alas that he could not continue as he began!</seg>
      </tuv>
